# Audapp Multi (Phase 21B) — compile-only multi-endpoint scaffold.
#
# Git policy (per Phase 21B decision): commit ONLY Audapp-owned files.
# The Microsoft-derived ACX AudioCodec sample source is intentionally NOT
# committed (licensing / provenance), matching the audapp-input scaffold.
# Those files live on-disk only and are reproduced by copying from
# driver/scaffold/audapp-input + applying the documented Phase 21B edits.
#
# Tracked (Audapp-owned): shared/Channels.h, project/.../AudioMulti.inf,
# build-multi.ps1, and the scaffold docs/scripts copied from audapp-input.

# --- Build artifacts / intermediates ---
Common/x64/
project/build/
project/out/
project/*.binlog
project/*.log
*.log
package/
**/x64/Debug/
**/x64/Release/

# --- Microsoft-derived ACX sample source (NOT committed) ---
Common/*.cpp
Common/*.h
Common/*.vcxproj
Common/*.vcxproj.*
inc/*.h
shared/Public.h
shared/Trace.h
project/upstream-audiocodec/Device.cpp
project/upstream-audiocodec/Driver.cpp
project/upstream-audiocodec/DriverSettings.h
project/upstream-audiocodec/Resources.rc
project/upstream-audiocodec/ReadMe.txt
project/upstream-audiocodec/AudioCodec.sln
